Detailed Description

template<class TYPE>
template<typename U, template< class > class Constness>
class gaia::base::List< TYPE >::ListIterator< U, Constness >

Iterator for List. 

 // Create a list and insert string datum.
 List<String> lst;
 
 for (size_t i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
      lst.insert(lst.begin(), String::valueOf(i));
 }
 
 // Create a list iterator and set to the head of lst, string "99"
 List<String>::iterator iter = lst.begin();
 
 // Move backward to string "98"
 --iter;
 
 // Delete string "98" and point to "97"
 iter = lst.erase(iter);
